INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2013-01-23 02:53:08','2013-01-23 02:53:08','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2013-01-23 02:53:08','2013-01-23 02:53:08','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2013-01-23 02:53:08','2013-01-23 02:53:08','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/teddy/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','trash','open','open','','sample-page','','','2013-01-22 22:28:26','2013-01-23 03:28:26','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(3,1,'2013-01-23 02:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2013-01-23 02:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(4,1,'2013-01-22 22:25:07','2013-01-23 03:25:07','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">I sell condos and lofts between High Park and Carlaw Avenue, from St. Clair Avenue down to the Lake. </span>\r\n\r\n<a name=\"_GoBack\"></a><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Read the following excerpt from Freakonomics. </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>(link to three page pdf)</b></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Sell with me and your property will be marketed and sold as if it were my own.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">To learn more, </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Selling','','publish','closed','open','','selling','','','2013-01-22 22:25:07','2013-01-23 03:25:07','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=4',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2013-01-22 22:24:57','2013-01-23 03:24:57','','Selling','','inherit','closed','open','','4-revision','','','2013-01-22 22:24:57','2013-01-23 03:24:57','',4,'http://localhost/teddy/4-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(6,1,'2013-01-22 22:25:31','2013-01-23 03:25:31','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">There is no selling in helping a person buy a condo or loft. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Buying a condo or loft the smart way requires having a fully detailed and comprehensive knowledge of the following components:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">What sizes, layouts, building ages, maintenance fees and taxes, amenities, locations, ect are available,</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">What you want (size, layout, style, building age, preferred maintenance fees and taxes, amenities, location, etc.)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">What you can afford </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">What your budget can buy you </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Your lifestyle </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Your long term plans</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">With this knowledge, drawing on my experience of having been inside over 300 buildings in the downtown core, I can find you what you want and save you time and money in the process. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">To discover the best buildings and units available in Toronto that meet your specific needs and desires, </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Buying','','publish','closed','open','','buying','','','2013-01-22 22:25:31','2013-01-23 03:25:31','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2013-01-22 22:25:28','2013-01-23 03:25:28','','Buying','','inherit','closed','open','','6-revision','','','2013-01-22 22:25:28','2013-01-23 03:25:28','',6,'http://localhost/teddy/6-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2013-01-22 22:25:46','2013-01-23 03:25:46','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">If you’d like to expand on your investment portfolio or increase the value of your savings account, I can show you how investing in Toronto core real estate can start earning you 7%-15% returns in less than one fiscal quarter, irrespective of market conditions.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">To learn more, </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">.</span>','Investing','','publish','closed','open','','investing','','','2013-01-22 22:25:46','2013-01-23 03:25:46','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2013-01-22 22:26:04','2013-01-23 03:26:04','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">The average Torontonian enters less than 10 condos or lofts a year. People who don’t work in real estate, especially outside of the condo and loft market, know very little about the condos and lofts in Toronto, regardless of the open houses they have strolled through or the “research they’ve conducted online.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">While listings can provide you with basic information about a property like the price, maintenance fees and property taxes - you may not be able to interpret vital information contained in a listing sheet. Additionally, you can’t compare a listing to other units in a building effectively without knowing the layout of the building, future development plans around the building and knowledge of past sales in the building and surrounding neighborhood. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Listings are too frequently misleading to prospective buyers and sellers. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">To learn how to use listings as the powerful tool they are, </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">. </span>','Listings','','publish','closed','open','','listings','','','2013-01-22 22:26:04','2013-01-23 03:26:04','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2013-01-22 22:26:21','2013-01-23 03:26:21','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Renting a place for 2-3 years is an excellent way to spend $40,000-$80,000K and have nothing but a bunch of U-Haul boxes and some packing tape at the end of occupancy to show for it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Obviously, if you can’t afford a condo or loft, you still need a roof over your head and renting is the best viable option, next to a friend’s couch.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">However, if you’re going to rent to “learn about the area before you buy” or to “see where the market goes” you have a lack of market knowledge which only helps wealthy people stay wealthy.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">If you’d like that knowledge, </span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">. </span>','Renting','','publish','closed','open','','renting','','','2013-01-22 22:26:21','2013-01-23 03:26:21','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2013-01-22 22:26:46','2013-01-23 03:26:46','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">It’s beyond me how realtors suggest using online mortgage calculators and other financial estimators.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Three of the city’s top mortgage brokers and financial planners are headquartered on the second floor of my office. I provide my clients with their services at no cost. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">With their help, you’ll be abreast of every financial option available to you and you will be provided with an accurate, current assessment of your financial footing. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">When you have facts in hand, you have confidence and an advantage.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">To get professional and transparent financial advice</span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\"><b>, contact me</b></span><span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Finance Tools','','publish','closed','open','','finance-tools','','','2013-01-22 22:26:46','2013-01-23 03:26:46','',0,'http://localhost/teddy/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(12,1,'2013-01-22 22:26:44','2013-01-23 03:26:44','<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">It’s beyond me how realtors suggest using online mortgage calculators and other financial estimators.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">Three of the city’s top mortgage brokers and financial planners are headquartered on the second floor of my office. I provide my clients with their services at no cost. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Garamond, serif;\">With their help, you’ll be abreast of every financial option available to you and you will be provided with an accurate, current assessment of your financial footing. </span>\n\n<